Class CompanyInfo.Builder

java.lang.Object
pl.lib.model.CompanyInfo.Builder
Enclosing class:
CompanyInfo
public static class CompanyInfo.Builder extends Object
Builder for CompanyInfo class implementing Builder pattern.

Enables step-by-step building of CompanyInfo object with optional fields.
